{"tid":799091,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得恆生管理學院-係一場學術界既投資騙局？","createTime":"2018-08-29T19:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T23:21:03.000Z","uid":125193,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1783fdff9d3bc35ee19110675df2e259ea87b223","tid":799091,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:25:41.000Z","msg":"院校環境就夠大<br />\n但學費就年年加，人數年年吹奏5000人<br />\n每年都吹奏升格大學但卻係年年不了了之<br />\n所謂既學術研究成果跟本言多過實<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇依間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6c9fdf96b9984f8297183bbe6f2618a7a6c270","tid":799091,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>院校環境就夠大<br />\n但學費就年年加，人數年年吹奏5000人<br />\n每年都吹奏升格大學但卻係年年不了了之<br />\n所謂既學術研究成果跟本言多過實<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇依間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"850f7216199faa248d99579a9e51e1efad11ca24","tid":799091,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>院校環境就夠大<br />\n但學費就年年加，人數年年吹奏5000人<br />\n每年都吹奏升格大學但卻係年年不了了之<br />\n所謂既學術研究成果根本<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>言多過實<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇依間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6c94768a2f40b2bb307bb27c030b0408c9cb055b","tid":799091,"uid":71147,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:28:26.000Z","msg":"一直都覺得讀完出嚟係做倫敦金弋堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ec53e83c012071a92c0a460f34c871738063ef","tid":799091,"uid":175598,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:30:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pi